Mobile phone numbers[edit]

There are currently four mobile network operators in Egypt: Orange, Vodafone, Etisalat, and We (by Telecom Egypt).

Operator Code Example (local) Example (international)
Vodafone 10 010-xxxx-xxxx +20-10-xxxx-xxxx
Etisalat 11 011-xxxx-xxxx +20-11-xxxx-xxxx
Orange 12 012-8100-4226 +20-12-xxxx-xxxx
We 15 015-xxxx-xxxx +20-15-xxxx-xxxx

Description Number format
